data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET!!!**Seller is  offering up to $5,000 towards buyers closing costs with acceptable offer** Bright and spacious 5 bedroom 4 bath pool home in the community of Sandy Ridge! Situated on a cul-de-sac, this home features 2 master suites one on each floor! As you enter the home, you will notice the high ceilings that lend an expansive and open feel with plenty of natural light to the formal living and dining room area. The room feels both grand and welcoming. On the first floor you have one primary bedroom with an en-suite with a garden tub, and separate shower. You will also find another bedroom downstairs with access to the guest bathroom. The kitchen offers white cabinets and plenty of storage. The family room is off the kitchen and leads out to the patio. Upstairs you have the second floor primary bedroom also with an en-suite with a garden tub, and separate shower. There are 2 additional bedrooms that share a Jack and Jill bathroom. Out back you will find a large enclosed pool with an extended deck overlooking conservation providing privacy. The lot provides an abundance of outdoor space, creating a sense of exclusivity and room to breathe. Lush greenery provided by the conservation enhance the natural beauty of the surroundings. With ample space for outdoor activities and landscaping, this exceptional lot offers a unique opportunity for both relaxation and outdoor enjoyment. There are many upgrades including new roof (2022),  new pool pump (2019), pool heater (2019), pool patio re-screened (2023), recently painted inside and out (2023), and new carpet (2023). Make your appointment today.
